channel.title: Wilderness Home (PI)
channel.description:
Hi guys,
On my PI source, I am trying to make Yanille as my Home instead of Edgeville... But when I teleported there using a ::tele command, I found out that Yanille is currently Wilderness Area... How do I make it so it's not wilderness anymore? I don't want people killing other people at the home...
I have checked my isinmulti in client.java and everything, but it only shows ardougne and others, not Yanille...
Please help.
All help is appreciated

item.title: Wilderness Home (PI)
item.dc:creator: @Get_Blitz Get Blitz
item.description:
@Get_Blitz wrote:

Try searching for “InWild” not sure where probably in playerassistant or CombatAssistant

Then look at the coords if they contain Yanille then just delete that line.
